sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>8081/TCP health
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    participant Route as OpenShift Router
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant API as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as NVIDIA NVCR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Route: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (Raw KServe)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review<br/>TLS (cert-manager)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (validate name length,<br/>block protected namespace)
        K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create metrics Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Note over Route: External access via OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS reencrypt/edge
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,Authorino: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Auth Setup
        User->>K8sAPI: POST LLMInferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (LLMInferenceService)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (HTTPRoute-scoped)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Gateway)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (TLS bootstrap)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Gateway-scoped)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Note over Authorino: Envoy proxy → Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC mTLS<br/>Service account CA
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over User,NVCR: Flow 3: NIM Account Integration
        User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review (singleton check)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Account)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: API key bearer
        NGC-->>Controller: Key validated
        Controller->>NGC: Fetch model catalog<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: NGC token
        NGC-->>Controller: Model catalog data
        Controller->>NVCR: Get registry token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: API key
        NVCR-->>Controller: Registry OAuth token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create pull Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime Template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Dashboard,API: Flow 4: Gateway Discovery (model-serving-api)
        Dashboard->>API: GET /api/v1/gateways?namespace=X<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (FIPS)<br/>Auth: User bearer token
        API->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: User bearer token
        K8sAPI-->>API: Access decision
        alt Access granted
            API->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
            K8sAPI-->>API: Gateway list
            API-->>Dashboard: JSON: gateway list<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        else Access denied
            API-->>Dashboard: JSON: empty results<br/>(no error - prevents info leakage)
        end
    end
